{"tid":2010451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(和理非必做)警甴商場終極攬炒攻略","createTime":"2020-05-10T11:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T12:15:53.000Z","uid":335967,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5ce30e5fadfe463a9fdab8f827e707dde0d55a","tid":2010451,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"係商場嘅黃店買定嘢飲嘢食先，等到狗入黎就做路人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迫狗攬炒圍觀嘅顧客</span></span>，或者去餐廳/food court排隊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">迫狗攬炒埋啲食客</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔使帶標語旗幟，費事畀狗入，總之叫口號唱歌咩都好，總之喺商場所有人都係顧客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f252e99a9ce3dcfebc84755d6f9b51f6b81bb7fb","tid":2010451,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d4a78dd126729d8fd0fee8e63104fc4f1dc6b3","tid":2010451,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:57:40.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"50923df9aba5cc18a48444a54be3ff50e90142bb","tid":2010451,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6a129c0949c28116a7a0094fa67b21b23c47f62a","tid":2010451,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:58:14.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0456f94218fa93aa390529c70d2d264bc92a75d3","tid":2010451,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco